SH-001 MEDIUM: Unauthenticated Pipeline Trigger\\n\\n**Location:** Lines 139-155
 \\n**Severity:** MEDIUM  \\n**Issue:** POST `/api/run` has no authentication. A
nyone with network access can trigger the trading pipeline.\\n\\n**Impact:**\\n-
